# PwnDrive Academy: Week 3 - Full Penetration Testing Write-up

## 🎯 Project Overview
This repository documents the security assessment and exploitation of the **PwnDrive** server (`10.150.150.11`). The assessment covers network reconnaissance, web enumeration, exploitation of broken access controls, and achieving Remote Code Execution (RCE).

